        "@value": "Thruster"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "A Jet Engine that is designed to use only stored Rocket Propellant to form a high speed propulsive jet in order to generate Thrust."
      }
    ],
