    "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Hard to give a definition for. Intuitively a \"natural kind\" rather than a collection of any old things, which a class is able to be, formally. At the meta level, universals are defined as positives, are disjoint with their siblings, have single asserted parents."
