        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Modified, originally from Mathias Brochhausen (D-Acts), http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0021009 . Equivalent to some Social Act that either 'legally revokes' some 'deontic role' OR 'has_specified_output' some 'deontic role'"
      }
