        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Schlosser, Markus, \"Agency\", The Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy (Winter 2019 Edition), Edward N. Zalta (ed.), available at: https://plato.stanford.edu/archives/win2019/entries/agency/"
