  {
    "@id": "https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000016",
    "@type": [
      "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Identification Artifact"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf": [
      {
        "@id": "https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00000798"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Identity Document"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "An Information Bearing Artifact that is the bearer of some Designative Information Content Entity and is the bearer of some Credential Role."
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "A passport"
      },
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "A bank statement"
      }
    ],
    "https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001754": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Modified significantly. Originally by Amanda Hicks (D-Acts; http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0020021) as 'identity document', which was a subclass of 'document', which is a Information Content Entity rather than an information bearing artifact. This is a critical difference. Moreover, the associated class having to do with 'documented identity' (another ICE) is obviated by CCO's Designative Information Content Entity. Original definition: \"A document that denotes some identity and is concretized by the bearer of some credential role.\" It was a defined class, equivalent to: IAO_0000310 and (IAO_0000136 some 'documented identity') and (RO_0000058 some (BFO_0000020 and (RO_0000052 some (RO_0000053 some 'credential role')))) and (RO_0000058 only (BFO_0000020 and (RO_0000052 some (RO_0000053 some 'credential role'))))"
      }
    ],
    "https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001760": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI",
        "@value": "https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts"
      }
    ],
    "https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001762": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Jonathan M. Vajda"
      }
    ]
  },
